description: Located on the Eastside, prime City Point neighborhood within a few blocks to the M Street Beach!  Wonderful turnkey Investment and/or Owner opportunity within a top, desirable rental market!  This 2017 gut renovated 2 family home features 4 levels of living space with condo quality finishes throughout.  Both bi-level units offer hardwood floors, custom kitchens, spacious islands, quartz countertops & SS appliances, open concept Living Room and Kitchen. Unit 1 bi-level has 4 bedrooms with 2 full baths and Unit 2 has an ensuite with 2 additional bedrooms & full bath.  Units are separately metered except for water/sewer.  In-unit laundry, FHA/gas, Central Air, unit 1 private patio & unit 2 private roof deck complete this amazing investment.  Centrally located this home is a commuters delight to downtown Boston & Seaport District or sit back and enjoy the comforts of what South Boston has to offer from restaurants/cafes to wind surfing at the beach.
